  "description": "A wide-angle daytime shot depicts a bustling harbor scene. Several white and red ships, including what appear to be tugboats and fishing vessels, are docked along a concrete pier. Large, industrial cranes dominate the backdrop, suggesting a working port. A low, white and dark grey railing runs across the foreground, partially obscuring the view but also providing a framing element. A weathered concrete pillar with dark stripes is visible on the right side of the frame. The sky is a pale blue with scattered clouds. The scene conveys a sense of maritime activity and industrial functionality.",
